EU’s Barroso Says Debt Crisis ‘Serious’; EU Has Solutions

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   S t e a r n s
-- 
2011-09-28T07:13:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/eu-s-barroso-says-debt-crisis-serious-eu-has-solutions.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  said the euro area’s debt crisis is “serious,” and
 Europe ’s leaders have solutions. He spoke today to the European
Parliament in Strasbourg,  France .  To contact the reporter on this story:
